<meta charset="UTF-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1" />
<title></title>
<style type="text/css">html{height:100%;}
body{background:#f3f7fa;width:100%;height:100%;min-width:100%;padding:0;margin:0;}
.blue{color:#64b8e7;}
.found-password-wrap{width:100%;height:100%;}
.found-password-box{width:80%;background:#fff;margin:0 auto;position:relative;}
.found-password-box>div{margin:5% 5% 15%;}
.found-password-box .title{font-size:20px;text-align:center;color:#38b3ee;margin-bottom:30px;}
.found-password-box .app-info{margin-bottom:20px;}
.found-password-box .app-icon{width:80px;height:80px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:15px;}
.found-password-box .app-name{font-size:20px;vertical-align:middle;}
.found-password-box .user-name{padding-right:5px;}
.found-password-box p{font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.found-password-box .footer{position:absolute;bottom:20px;margin:0;padding:0;width:100%;height:14px;line-height:14px;color:#bbbbbb;text-align:center;font-size:12px;}
.found-password-box .footer a{color#bbb;}
.found-password-box .footer a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
.found-password-form .form-wrap{width:300px;margin:0 auto;}
.found-password-form .btn-num4{width:100%;}
.found-password-form .app-info{width:80px;height:80px;margin:0 auto 20px;}
.found-password-form .title{font-size:18px;}
.reset-success-tip .form-wrap{display:none;}
.reset-success-tip>div {margin:0!important;}
.reset-success-tip .reset-success{display:block;}
.found-password-form .reset-success .user-email{font-size:18px;padding-top:10px;}
.found-password-form .reset-success p{font-size:26px;}

.error span{padding-top:14px;display:inline-block;}

@media all and (min-width:320px) and (max-width: 414px){
    .found-password-box{width:90%;}
    .found-password-box>div{margin:5% 15px 15%;}
    .error{margin-top:20px;}
}
@media all and (width:320px){
    .found-password-form .form-wrap{width:260px;}
    .found-password-form .reset-success{width:260px;}
}
</style>
<div class="found-password-wrap sys-flex sys-flex-center">
    <div class="found-password-box">
        <div>
            <p class="title">重置<span class="user-account">{email}</span>账号密码</p>

            <div class="app-info">
                <span class="app-name">{appname}</span>
            </div>

            <p><span class="user-name blue">{membername}</span>用户，您好：</p>

            <p>点击下面的链接确认你的电子邮件地址，并重置你的账户密码。重置密码链接：</p>

            <p><a class="blue" href="{link_url}">{link_url}</a></p>

            <p>此链接有效期为24小时，请在有效期内进行修改，每天至多允许找回5次密码。如果此重置密码请求非你本人所发，请忽略 本邮件。如果以上链接无法点击，请将它复制到你的浏览器（如chrome）地址栏中进入访问。</p>

            <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
